{"tid":806523,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[CS:GO] 倫敦FACEIT MAJOR - CHALLENGERS STAGE 討論區","createTime":"2018-09-04T17:35:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-10T03:06:44.000Z","uid":56879,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0e15ea7d475ea09f25be979c418d3dce85a8f325","tid":806523,"uid":56879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T17:35:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.hltv.org/images/galleries/1693-full/1519304709.0183.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hltv.org%2Fimages%2Fgalleries%2F1693-full%2F1519304709.0183.jpeg&h=2d593e08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一年兩度CSGO Major又黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由上次ELEAGUE Boston開始 Majorj都會分為兩部份: Challengers Stage 同 Legends Stage<br />\n<br />\n聽日香港時間5點開始既就係Challengers Stage, 係呢個Stage 16隊入面既頭8隊就會晉級到Legends Stage同上次Major既頭8位爭今次Major既冠軍<br />\n <br />\n換言知, 係呢個STAGE既目標只係晉級, 冇所謂羸輸之分<br />\n<br />\n廢話少講, 首先自貼我既Pick'Em<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/k45433Faceit%20Cngerq44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fk45433Faceit%2520Cngerq44.jpg&h=3b1df72c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n16隊就由大熱開始講起<br />\n<br />\n1) Astralis<br />\n而家既世界一哥, 由Magiskboy代替左Snakerbye個位開始, 成隊野就變返以前聞風喪膽打極唔撚死既Astralis<br />\n由戰術執行, 到隊員默契, 個人能力都係冠絕而家Challengers Stage同Legends Stage既所有隊伍<br />\n上屆Major因為有成幾個月既時間都冇同傷左既dev1ce夾過, 爆大冷Group Stage出局導致今次要由Challengers Stage開始打起<br />\n但賭J都得今次應該3-0/3-1輕鬆屌入下一輪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2) Optic<br />\n丹麥二/三哥, 早幾個禮拜黎過香港電莖節而且首輪出局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 既Optic Gaming亦都係今次既出線大大大熱之一, 原因亦唔洗多講: Konfig, CajunB, Jugi +Snappi+Gade, 整體能力基本上係呢16隊入面既TOP 3, 必睇既係首次打Major既Jugi, 個人認為枝AWP比dev1ce更具威脅, 一定要留意下佢既打法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3) Liquid<br />\n每次Major都換幾次人既Liquid應該冇懸念可以出線, 由Taco加入開始已經睇得出佢地開始進入收成期, 加上有而家NA最TOP既NAF-FLY carry, 應該都係輕鬆晉級<br />\n<br />\n呢隊野既唯一隱憂就係由踢走jdm開始就變左nitro做awper, 而佢同時亦係隊伍既in-game leader, 加上nitro不嬲表現飄忽, 變相如果對住一啲有勁awper/CT side有紀律既隊就會處於下風, 但相信隊住Challengers Stage呢班垃圾都冇難度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61af663fa499788ac5e5314e638162f5a3019756","tid":806523,"uid":56879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T17:54:11.000Z","msg":"4) Gambit<br />\n前屆Krakow Major冠軍. 但走左靈魂人物Zeus, 事隔一年呢隊野仍然係未搵到igl<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除左XGOD影響之外, 呢隊野不嬲係換左新隊員個排會彈起, 而佢地最近就新請左之前打FLIPSID3既BLAD3黎做教練同新隊員mir<br />\n<br />\nGambit 今次出線與否, 絕對係取決於核心Hobbit+新隊員mir可唔可以打返佢地各自既正常水準, 個人認為佢地應該係勉強3-2出線既其中一隊<br />\n<br />\n5) BIG<br />\n前屆Krakow Major驚為天人, 除左利用jump bug之外, 其實都唔可以否認gob b帶住班廢人都入到頭8係有啲料到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n事隔一年, 隊伍換走左發揮極唔穩定既KEEV變成英國唯一職業玩家smooya做awper, <br />\n對於極度著重戰術既BIG黎講一枝穩定既awp係必需, 而且smooya除左穩定亦都可以aggressive地用awp拎entry, 絕對係睇高BIG一線既主要原因<br />\n<br />\n除此之外,亦都調走Legija去做教練加入中規中矩既rifler tizian, 呢條友屬於工兵類, 冇評價<br />\n<br />\n睇BIG識睇一定係睇gob b既臨場戰術+佢地既execute戰術+grenade既運用+有冇發現新bug<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢隊BIG除左對住火力強勁既Astralis/Optic/HellRaisers 應該都係無敵手<br />\n<br />\n6) Rogue<br />\n呢次Challengers Stage黎講如果要我揀黑馬一定係北美Rogue/中国Tyloo<br />\n基於對hiko既偏心所以都pick左呢隊Rogue<br />\n講就冇咩好講 因為佢地打法都係普通NA隊伍打法all aim no brain<br />\n睇下rickeh+cadian double awp既運用可唔可以殺出一條血路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df79698c7cda655e34379d0d96f6d1eabed10e74","tid":806523,"uid":56879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T17:58:30.000Z","msg":"7/8 Vega Squadron + Virtus Pro<br />\n呢兩隊都係新換陣容, 所以打成點, 打法係點, 全部都係未知之數<br />\n呢兩隊基本上都係面臨解散/大換血, 今次Major應該係佢地命運既分水嶺<br />\n出唔出到線就會睇佢地既做化<br />\n<br />\n值得一提Vega Squadron 2年前亦係係賽事大冷門既程況下將NIP 16-2踢左出局, 今次再碰頭睇下有冇機會有另一經典出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"542a59285ca9cc18a86770836a46d6389b96955b","tid":806523,"uid":3765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T17:59:57.000Z","msg":"今次好鐘意LONDON 個章<br />\n<br />\n所以一定要拎金牌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"588bbf66cda20bba64d684357c708bac5f7e3788","tid":806523,"uid":56879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T18:08:36.000Z","msg":"然後就到聽日第一輪我既分析:<br />\n<br />\n17:00 - Space Soldiers vs. <strong>Rogue</strong> <br />\n<br />\nKebab隊臨打前話NGIN拎唔到VISA所以冇得打, 雖然NGIN本身就係呢隊既最大弱點,<br />\n但相信換個COACH打會仲差, 所以應該Rogue ez win <br />\n<br />\n18:30 - Virtus.pro vs. <strong>NiP</strong><br />\n<br />\n反NIP唔解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n20:00 - <strong>Gambit</strong> vs. TYLOO<br />\n<br />\n55開, 兩隊都冇乜戰術可言, 所以都係靠對槍決勝, 可以留意兩位黎自印尼既現時亞洲Top 2選手BNTET+XCCURATE既發揮<br />\n<br />\n21:30 - <strong>BIG</strong> vs. Renegades<br />\n<br />\n輕鬆屌打澳洲佬<br />\n<br />\n23:00 - <strong>Vega Squadron</strong> vs. Spirit<br />\n<br />\n海軍鬥水手, 應該係全日最低質既賽事<br />\n<br />\n00:30 - <strong>North</strong> vs. HellRaisers<br />\n<br />\n狀態大勇既禿頭佬MSL應該可以先拔頭籌<br />\n<br />\n02:00 - Liquid vs. <strong>OpTic</strong><br />\n<br />\n全日重點, 55開, 等睇Jugi 打爆對面<br />\n<br />\n03:30 - <strong>Astralis</strong> vs. compLexity<br />\n冇懸念"},{"pid":"5c2afeff84ce2c39985bff8430913bd34f0d48e0","tid":806523,"uid":56879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"542a59285ca9cc18a86770836a46d6389b96955b","tid":806523,"uid":3765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T17:59:57.000Z","msg":"今次好鐘意LONDON 個章<br />\n<br />\n所以一定要拎金牌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T18:09:24.000Z","msg":"其實都係3角型都上次冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40592eacec49ae5cfac457b67f51f90717eb6cb8","tid":806523,"uid":134774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T18:10:36.000Z","msg":"winstrike 係legend 但astralis係challenger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主好有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1907edf6a7ae8c4d394d3768d52ae9592f9e25bc","tid":806523,"uid":3765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c2afeff84ce2c39985bff8430913bd34f0d48e0","tid":806523,"uid":56879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"542a59285ca9cc18a86770836a46d6389b96955b","tid":806523,"uid":3765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T17:59:57.000Z","msg":"今次好鐘意LONDON 個章<br />\n<br />\n所以一定要拎金牌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T18:09:24.000Z","msg":"其實都係3角型都上次冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T18:11:58.000Z","msg":"次次都一樣架啦<br />\n<br />\n我貪london 個字眼"},{"pid":"31512879c55145c4bd3adf23a1c204362daaa60e","tid":806523,"uid":56879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40592eacec49ae5cfac457b67f51f90717eb6cb8","tid":806523,"uid":134774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T18:10:36.000Z","msg":"winstrike 係legend 但astralis係challenger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主好有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T18:14:15.000Z","msg":"拿, 又冇得咁講<br />\n上次QBF的確大勝VP, COMEBACK OT羸左GAMBIT, 同係半場TRAIN 13-2落後既情況下COMEBACK左MOUSESPORTS<br />\n以佢地上次既表現應該都冇得話係咩運氣成份<br />\n<br />\n而ASTRALIS上次的確係冇隊型全部人不在狀態<br />\n加上VALVE今次改制 0-3出局既下次唔會自動CHALLENGER STAGE留位, 應該唔會再有上次BIG既情況出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b64ffd50d32e65bc223c399f60c475589f75707","tid":806523,"uid":124891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T18:20:59.000Z","msg":"Mouz champion"},{"pid":"393ffd39b7e80b024d4e141cfa215cc03cc37f57","tid":806523,"uid":44210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T18:50:26.000Z","msg":"Mouz <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89c07168b64e02bcfdc47241f0a6d0355f7ff783","tid":806523,"uid":56879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"393ffd39b7e80b024d4e141cfa215cc03cc37f57","tid":806523,"uid":44210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T18:50:26.000Z","msg":"Mouz <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T00:28:55.000Z","msg":"今次major 3大熱門 astralis navi mouz<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffdcdfa92e74f890dc1f43f61e387b99318a67af","tid":806523,"uid":56879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T08:34:32.000Z","msg":"仲有半個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ad9ab997674453fb9f268e05c3dfddbe2ed6824","tid":806523,"uid":35007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T08:46:09.000Z","msg":"#ToTheStars <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cef45c8ce956ac2cf46bb16f35e7bee2d67797d","tid":806523,"uid":151347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T09:27:06.000Z","msg":"點解唔講下north既 ???<br />\ndreamhack master羸到一哥astralis<br />\n照計黎到major<br />\n個prepartion應該都係差唔多 north可以走得更遠"},{"pid":"6aca2e4ea5c9c6cbb513efc32add283bca6a4c52","tid":806523,"uid":3381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T10:14:13.000Z","msg":"開波未"},{"pid":"1e3ec2b9c6c10ba83b7ac33202efc77f88afba43","tid":806523,"uid":3765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T10:14:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/faceittv\" data-sr-url=\"http